{"id":111247,"type":2,"name":"Mater's Tall Tales Season 1","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b3/60/111247_AA12i.jpg","rating":{"total":6,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":1,"5":0,"6":3,"7":1,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5.3},"summary":"　　“我要是撒谎，出门就被车撞！（If I'm lyin', I'm cryin'.）”，这是小拖车拖线（康康 台湾引进版配音）的口头禅。虽然他信誓旦旦地保证，但是关于他的故事总是那么离奇。比如，拖线自称做过特技明星、消防车、私家侦探、外太空拖车、斗牛士、医生、漂移车手、重金属歌手、摔角冠军，甚至还遇到过外星飞碟。他的讲述离奇非常，因此麦昆理所当然不买账。不过，似乎麦昆总会成为拖线那些故事的见证人。是真？是假？别管那么多了，权且随着拖线开怀大笑吧！ \r\n 　　《拖线狂想曲》为皮克斯继《赛车总动员》后，以配角拖线为主角制作的系列动画短片，供迪斯尼电视频道播放。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>拖线狂想曲第一季</li><li><span>话数: </span>3</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/22013\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">John Lasseter</a></li><li><span>脚本: </span><a href=\"/person/22013\">John Lasseter</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/7960\">Pixar Animation Studios</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>2008年10月27日</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":14,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"pixar","count":5},{"name":"欧美","count":4},{"name":"短片","count":2},{"name":"TV","count":2},{"name":"美国","count":1},{"name":"2008","count":1},{"name":"3D","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":424257,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/424257","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":424258,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/424258","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":424259,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/424259","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":22013,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d6/bd/22013_prsn_O1jC2.jpg","name":"约翰·拉塞特","desc":"导演"},{"id":7960,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f5/55/7960_prsn_UD3i1.jpg","name":"皮克斯动画工作室","desc":"动画制作"}],"relations":[{"id":111248,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/94/fe/111248_9tZ79.jpg","title":"Mater's Tall Tales Season 2","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/111248"},{"id":36828,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f7